        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-60677d8c-56d0-460a-adfb-9387ea4c8611">
                The Lord Privy Seal (Sir John Anderson)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-60677d8c-56d0-460a-adfb-9387ea4c8611" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
