<p class="">Could my right hon. Friend indicate the type of projectile that he has in his mind against which underground protection should be provided?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-15947e9b-cab0-4b0f-8a3b-93bce8990f14" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
