<p class="">What about the effect on the public mind of people being killed in the street? If hon. Members will compare that with the effect on the public mind of a disaster in a coal mine or a factory or on a railway, they will see the bearing of the point I am making.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
