<p class="">How many mothers and young children, I wonder, might be killed in one of the big shelters? My argument ought to be considered as a whole. I am trying to give a connected statement, and, apart from the interruptions, I am doing so.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
