<p class="">I was perfectly clear about that. I understand that, but I do not see signs of a decision as to the long-term policy or the possibility of 100 per cent. protection against high explosives. It is admitted by the right hon. Gentleman that there has not yet been any de- <span id="1334" class="column-number" data-column-number="1334"></span> cision on that point, but he rather indicated that he is enthusiastic about that line of policy.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
