<p class="">I do not think that any of these matters come under this Vote at all.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6f79cb3e-841b-4582-9a1b-a8781596ff9e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
