    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will my right hon. Friend look into the question of whether the smaller badge can be worn?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-20159d32-faf9-464e-a085-7ec79df79151" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-03-01/debates/63a19bcf-64c2-4541-8328-fc5ab72768e8/PrivySealOffice#contribution-20159d32-faf9-464e-a085-7ec79df79151">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
